Functional requirements of virtual university :-

1.A university will have colleges, enroll the students.
  University will conduct the exams and after evaluation, result will be declared.
2.All Colleges are affiliated to a university. Students take admission to college.
4.College offers courses like Btech,Mtech,MBA,MCA,BBA, BCA etc and students opt for a course whatever the college possess.
3.Faculty will teach students and take the attendance of all the students.
5.Sometime lecture can be taken by HOD of particular department.
6.Principal controls and manages the whole college.
7.There are some departments and single HOD is associated to it.
8.Periodic exams are taken in college like monthly test and after evaluation, results are declared.
